data.description: The perfect place to start your journey into homeownership! The home inspection has already been completed by the sellers, so you can move in quicker and with more money in your pocket! This home features 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with a potential 3rd bedroom in the basement. Both bathrooms have been updated with heated tile floors! The main floor has an open layout with an ample amount of space in the kitchen, and the yard is fully fenced and ready for your furry friends to explore.  Additional updates include many new windows and laminate flooring throughout the main floor. With a 2 stall detached garage and lots of storage, this home is ready for its new owners to make it their own!
